--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, <airly2002@h...> wrote:
> Windlord:
> 
> "KENZO!!!"said windlord while he took off "Do you think that we
could >reach the cannon before the Unicrons minions????"
"Theres a good chance that we can.  They are coming all the way from
outer space after all."  He said to Windlord as he flew along.
As they reached the cannon site just in time to hear the end of
Rodimus's speech, as well as Hydras's interruption.  Kenzo landed and
transformed back to his robot form. He then glanced around at all the
different types of bots that were gathered together.  It looked like a
strange Halloween party.
"Looks like we'll get to meat a lot of 'old friends'" Kenzo commented.

Inferno and Quickstrike arrived from the opposite direction.  
"Ah! The Queen as summoned bots from every colony.  A show of the
Royalty's power." Inferno stated, even if it was a bit inaccurate.
Quickstrike sat down panting "I-I musta run at least 40 miles. I need
a break." he collapsed on the ground to catch his breath.

Waspinator flew nearby carrying the missile he had taken from the
Predacon base.  He placed it nearby on the ground before proceeding to
the gathering.
"He-he, for once Waspinator be sneaky one.  Waspinator will blast
Mini-Unicrons warriors with bomb so they know how it feels. hehehe."
He snickered to himself.
